# Domain-based rewrites: each imprint URL serves its own subfolder transparently.
# The URL in the browser stays as the imprint domain.
# Status 200! = rewrite (URL preserved). The trailing ! forces it.

# Dropthorn Press
https://dropthorn.com/*       /dropthorn-press/:splat  200!
https://www.dropthorn.com/*   /dropthorn-press/:splat  200!
http://dropthorn.com/*        /dropthorn-press/:splat  200!
http://www.dropthorn.com/*    /dropthorn-press/:splat  200!

